title: Merril Bainbridge - The Garden (1996)
description: This is Merril Bainbridge's 1996 album The Garden. I searched for this album for a long time and the only version I was able to acquire was a flac version and it was horribly choppy. I finally decided to take some initiative and rip the songs and upload the album myself. The last track Garden In My Room (Reprise) is pretty choppy, but the rest of the tracks are decent quality especially considering the album is nowhere else to be found. Enjoy!
